            <title>清明临近，纸扎版小米SU7、特斯拉、三折叠、扫地机都出现了…</title>
            <link>https://www.36kr.com/p/3223115035544450</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.36kr.com/p/3223115035544450</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 00:15:51 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p>近日，有网友称在丧葬用品店发现了纸扎的小米SU7，网友调侃称小米“打通了阴阳两界”。</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_e62cd866565d4c9e9f2ad88273e4ab5d@000000_oswg93062oswg1080oswg601_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>看到这则消息，笔者第一反应是意外，竟然还可以这样。于是便上电商平台搜索发现，还真有纸扎版小米SU7。</p>
  <p>本以为祭祀用品，无非就是烧一些纸钱，最多就是印有几百、几千亿的冥钞，没想到“祭祀业”发展到今天，早就今非昔比。</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_32bab9e6c4e1457bb1e8e8bc7482fcb6@000000_oswg107204oswg1080oswg1728_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_6ca82461914c4f4ea702361995fb22bd@000000_oswg141008oswg1080oswg1728_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_29612cb28a2349df8d830c5ea68ba933@000000_oswg165481oswg1080oswg1837_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>先来看纸扎版SU7，在电商平台上能搜到不少祭祀版小米SU7，售价也不贵，十几二十几元不等。</p>
  <p>从卖家发的照片来看，纸扎版小米SU7仿真度还是挺高的，有天窗、方向盘、还印了驾驶员。</p>
  <p>笔者寻思，既然都有纸扎版SU7了，国内一众新势力会不会也有专门祭祀的纸扎版呢？</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_a2cc1abc187c419f9a8bb6ed60b140de@000000_oswg189106oswg1080oswg1672_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_c9bb5e7d3e6c4ca08361922d0abb1ab7@000000_oswg189985oswg1080oswg1751_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_88060f814e6c4183b0562f08d4dd3bab@000000_oswg222607oswg1080oswg1706_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>结果搜索一圈发现，除了小米汽车外，并没有商家在卖纸扎版的新势力品牌，反倒是不少卖家在卖纸扎版特斯拉汽车。</p>
  <p>和纸扎版SU7类似，纸扎版特斯拉也做的很逼真，不仅有驾驶员，甚至还特地配备了充电桩。</p>
  <p>笔者发现，纸扎版的电车品牌很少，除了小米和特斯拉外基本没有；但纸扎版的知名油车非常多。</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_d7ab9cc2afd7445ea67c5e323f6ead1c@000000_oswg366334oswg1080oswg2192_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_4a61d65264544876859185d8a4e1f41c@000000_oswg202714oswg1080oswg1693_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_3d91ebbb598f4ac3a0daeb289ece5d26@000000_oswg211934oswg1080oswg1908_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>比如纸扎版的奔驰大G、宾利、劳斯莱斯、迈巴赫等。所以，纸扎版的新能源品牌目前尚属“蓝海市场”。</p>
  <p>既然都能给列祖列宗烧车了，是不是也能让他们享受下更多现代科技产品？</p>
  <p>当然可以，安排：</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_f8823d8315b4425b8c253b2d25f659c7@000000_oswg108191oswg1080oswg1676_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_9dd6323510254229ba626727a4c1538a@000000_oswg224533oswg1080oswg1947_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>先来一架“冥航A380”纸扎版私人飞机；</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_8e9313f4e48547e2a0727838ea809bf1@000000_oswg230063oswg1080oswg1951_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_cc83d605f82e484092375a1cd7bfd3fc@000000_oswg238924oswg1080oswg1713_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>再来一部纸扎版三折叠手机，各种App必须都装上；</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_b7789bdc1b444af990b1603e817476cb@000000_oswg308593oswg1080oswg2181_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_34e75bfc07a84e4d926ce31c64e7d653@000000_oswg304195oswg1080oswg2080_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>还有各种纸扎版扫地机器人，甚至连电影《星际穿越》中的机器人TARS都有纸扎版；</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_24125169f7d54bed84f0e4cea9125ce0@000000_oswg163912oswg1080oswg1631_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_59dffdf251c54b158ea431f599947d38@000000_oswg293025oswg1080oswg2030_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>纸扎版电视、电脑必不可少，而且还是苹果Mac电脑；</p>
  <p class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img.36krcdn.com/hsossms/20250326/v2_a97d47ec66394114ab86296570164a3f@000000_oswg224484oswg1080oswg1713_img_000?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/interlace,1" /></p>
  <p>还有纸扎版按摩椅……</p>
  <p>总而言之，如今能买到非常多的各种用来祭祀的纸扎版产品，品类涵盖了生活的方方面面，几乎是你能想到的，就能买得到。</p>
  <p>但商家这么做可能涉嫌商标侵权。</p>
  <p>山东博睿律师事务所陈瑞福认为，冥用品如果有小米商标，则涉嫌侵犯商标权。但他也表示，“但从另一个角度也说明小米、保时捷等品牌热销，不会导致社会评价降低，上述做法虽不妥，但整体上不宜做侵权处理。”</p>
  <p>而陕西恒达律师事务所高级合伙人、公益律师赵良善表示，纸扎车在制作过程中使用小米商标和车型设计，从法律角度，涉及未经授权的侵权行为。商家生产和销售此类纸扎产品时，需要获得品牌方正式许可。消费者购买时也应选择正规授权产品，避免潜在的法律风险。</p>
  <p>马上就到清明祭祖的日子，笔者也该考虑是不是给列祖列宗烧部“三折叠”手机以寄哀思了。</p>
  <p>本文来自微信公众号<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2ODcwMDY2NA==&amp;mid=2247565966&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=9df66919ac33f93be537968e1e520bc7&amp;chksm=fd197cc16dee737119cca4732b6f9486d0ba962be879f87d482846ba1bf7ace7b5af773aad73&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">“三言财经”（ID：sycaijing）</a>，作者：三言Pro，36氪经授权发布。</p>
